<p>Assumption University exists for the main purpose of serving the nation by providing scientific and humanistic knowledge, particularly in the business education and management science through research and interdisciplinary approaches.</p>
<p>To this end it aims at forming intellectually competent graduates who :</p>
<ul>
<li>are morally sound, committed to acting justly, and open to further growth.&nbsp;</li>
