<p>In loyalty to its Christian mission, Assumption University stands for</p>
<ul>
<li>the inculcation of respect for the three institutions of the Nation: Religion, Country, the King and a democratic way of life.</li>
<li>the belief that a man justifies himself and his existence by the nobility of his work: <strong>LABOR OMNIA VINCIT</strong></li>
<li>the commitment to be a light that leads men towards the true source of all knowledge and life: <strong>LUX VERITAS</strong></li>
</ul>
